Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.690 --> 00:00:04.310
There ....there.......   I see him.....!!!

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:19.500
Glories to the one who holds conch 
and mace in his hands....... 

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:24.500
.......may he who is robed in yellow
garments give shelter at his lotus feet...

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:37.850
" nimai , nimai , get up son ! " (...glories 
to one who resides with the honest...)

00:00:42.190 --> 00:00:45.250
...... who is the only friend 
at end of our lives........

00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:54.160
........ may he grant me his lotus feet , 
who is the slayer of Kaliya serpent.........

00:01:01.190 --> 00:01:05.290
..... all praises to him who resides with his 
devotees and merciful to the miserable ...

00:01:06.310 --> 00:01:09.870
... may that achyuta , that eternal lord 
accept me at his lotus feet..........

00:01:11.130 --> 00:01:16.020
..... glories to the one who liberates the 
sinner and always abides by dharmaa....

00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:20.830
.... may he , the killer of demons grant 
me his lotus feet .........

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:30.610
" O lord , thakur , dont take away my 
husband from me !!......"

00:01:31.940 --> 00:01:33.710
".......... dont you see , the highest 
pandita crying like a child ?!! "

00:01:34.530 --> 00:01:36.560
"........ dont destroy our beautiful family !"

00:01:38.490 --> 00:01:40.920
" Vishnupriya , Vishnupriya , can you tell 
me where is he ? "

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:45.530
" Dont do like that , where will he go ?
Didnt you say that he is everywhere ?!... "

00:01:46.540 --> 00:01:49.490
"........Didnt you say that Krishna is 
within everyone's heart ? ...............

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:52.260
...........wherever there is Krishna naam , 
there is Krishna ?!!"

00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:56.550
" True .. true it is Vishnupriya."

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:04.160
"But why did the bard stop singing ? Let 
me go and ask them to sing once more ."

00:02:04.850 --> 00:02:07.420
"Please , please dont leave . Be calm."

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.940
"But why did the bards leave without 
singing Krishna naam ?"

00:02:10.510 --> 00:02:13.660
" I'll sit at your feet and do Krishna naam 
day and night ? You just take a seat "

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:18.980
" Okay Vishnupriya...I shall sit . But you 
must do Krishna naam "

00:02:22.330 --> 00:02:23.620
" Please leave now "

00:02:24.250 --> 00:02:25.830
" Wont we have a morsel of rice to eat ?"

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:30.580
"I shall give you as much rice as you want
 , but stop Krishna naam in this house !! "

00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:41.340
"Glories to the one who holds conch 
and mace in his hands....... "

00:03:28.260 --> 00:03:36.390
"........O Knowledge of the vedas , 
Radharaman , the treasure of Vrindavan.."

00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:42.450
"................give me shelter at you feet."

00:03:46.300 --> 00:03:50.860
"................at your lotus feet !!! "

